title: Kim- Family and Labour characteristics by Sex and Age Group
name: Kim- Family and Labour characteristics by Sex and Age Group
description: An annual representation of labour participation by both sexes.

properties.sex: Characteristics such as age are as of December 31 of the reference year.
The sex of the younger non-filing population is, in many cases, not known. For this reason, the information by sex does not add up to the total shown.
The participation rate of persons with labour income is the count of persons with labour income expressed as a percentage of the total taxfilers and dependants for the same area.
Total taxfilers and dependants by age group is available in CANSIM table 1110005.
